		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1790658601A1E187"]
			description: ["Now you can make the &lBending Machine&r! It's basically an improved Forge Hammer when it comes to plates, because now the ingot to plate ratio is 1:1 instead of 3:2!"]
			id: "69561C5FE389E808"
			subtitle: "Ben Dover"
