			title: "CMSA"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -2.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1790658601A1E187"]
			description: ["You might think, \"Quest book! I already have a steam extractor! Why would I need another one?\" Well, that's because the &lElectric Extractor&r can &9melt stuff&r! The molten stuff can later be solidifed in a Fluid Extractor, or used in an exclusive Assembler recipe, along with other stuff."]
			id: "6ECAC46D9A42C571"
			subtitle: "AND THEY EXTRACT IT! #2"
			tasks: [{
				id: "04FA62804E274E51"
