		{
			dependencies: [
				"21751E823716D187"
				"6ECAC46D9A42C571"
				"5E03AFFA39D5E340"
			]
			description: ["Using your &8Arc Furnace&r for annealed copper foil and your &aExtractor&r for liquid steel, you can combine them in an &cAssembler&r with some tin dust to make &lRectifiers&r! These will be used to make &9Decent Electronic Circuits&r, AKA your &9first LMV circuits&r."]
