			description: [
				"Who's ready for another big boy? I sure am, so good thing the &aElectric Blast Furnace&r is coming!"
				""
				"The &lElectric Blast Furace&r, or &oEBF&r, is a multiblock machine that serves as a big furnace that can smelt stuff at very high temperatures. It's &ostupidly&r useful. Right now, you'll want it so that you can smelt &3aluminium dust&r into ingots, as that is the material used to make &bMV&r machinery."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"The &bEBF&r is VERY energy hungry, so either upgrade your power generation or create a battery buffer."
				""
				"Also, it can make steel faster!"
			]
