			dependencies: ["75E908DD55EE9B55"]
			description: ["After shoving random stuff in your new &5Electrolyzer&r &o(or just browsing EMI for a bit)&r, you see that you can make &3aluminium dust&r by separating &1sapphire dust&r! It doesn't seem like you can smelt it in a &7furnace&r, though. Maybe you'll need something more &apowerful&r..."]
