				"10A99CBED28EC735"
			]
			description: ["Much like how &8steel&r was the main material of &7LV&r machines, &3aluminium&r will be the material of &bMV&r machines. Because of that, you will need a lot of it, and if you don't want to wait a while, you should probably leave it cooking in your &aEBF&r in the background while you do other stuff."]
