		{
			dependencies: ["1790658601A1E187"]
			description: [
				"The &lCentrifuge&r is a machine similar to the &9Electrolyzer&r because it also separates things, but the centrifuge separates things by spinning, while the electrolyzer uses electricity."
				""
				"But just because these two do the same thing, doesn't mean that you don't need one of them! The centrifuge and electrolyzer have different recipes that they can do."
				""
				"&9Note&r: Like the Assembler, the Centrifuge requires 4 circuits to make!"
			]
			id: "0FD5CCFA88F7C821"
			subtitle: "You spin me right round"
