		{
			dependencies: ["75E908DD55EE9B55"]
			description: [
				"You may notice that some machines now have &9fluids&r as inputs and outputs. You can't hold them in your hands, so how do you carry them around? The answer is with fluid cells and drums!"
				""
				"&7Fluid Cells&r are for amounts of fluids less than a bucket."
				"&6Drums&r are for amounts of fluids that are more than a bucket. They can be made out of various materials."
				""
				"To grab a fluid, click on the fluid slot with an empty fluid cell or drum."
				"To drop a fluid, click on the empty slot you want the fluid to go with a non empty fluid cell or drum."
				""
				"To carry acids use a gold drum!"
			]
