			]
			dependency_requirement: "one_completed"
			description: [
				"&lGallium&r is an element that you'll need to mix with arsenic to make &9gallium arsenide&r, to make &bMV&r circuits."
				""
				"You can make it in 2 ways: Make a &achemical bath&r and bathe crushed bauxite or sphalerite to obtain gallium at a 70% chance, or &eelectrolyse&r sphalerite dust to obtain gallium at a 7.5% chance."
				""
				"If you  are using the &eelectrolysation&r method, it might be a good idea to make a &achemical bath&r for a higher chance at obtaining gallium. Think of it as a long term investment!"
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"&9NOTE:&r You can unlock this quest by doing any of the dependency quests, you don't need all of them!"
			]
