			description: ["&lGallium Arsenide&r is a &overy important semiconductor&r that you will need for your first &bMV&r circuit components! Get it by making a mixer and mixing gallium and arsenic."]
			id: "0CDC3425006E627F"
			subtitle: "Circuit Maker"
