		{
			dependencies: ["1790658601A1E187"]
			description: [
				"The &lMixer&r is a machine that mixes stuff together!"
				""
				"&9&o\"But quest book... I can already mix stuff with my hands! Why do i need a dedicated machine for it?\"&r"
				""
				"Well, your hands aren't good enough for the things we're going to be mixing, like gallium and arsenic."
			]
