			dependencies: ["5E03AFFA39D5E340"]
			description: ["You are probably still feeding your boilers with either a primitive water pump or a mechanical pump. But both of these have downsides; The primitive pump is big, and the mechanical pump needs kinetic energy. Luckily, your new advances in technology have unlocked a new machine: The &9Aqueous accumulator&r. This machine, when put next to 2 water sources, will make water automatically! No energy required!"]
